hadithEnglish:
Ali said &ldquo;If I survive for the Christians of Banu Taghlib I shall kill fighters and captivate children for I had written a document between them and the Prophet(ﷺ) to the effect that they would not make their children Christian.

Abu Dawud said &ldquo;This is rejected (munkar) tradition and it has reached me from Ahmad (bin Hanbal) that he used to reject this tradition seriously.

Abu Ali said &ldquo;Abu Dawud did not present this (tradition) in this second reading.&rdquo;
